description: This hall of fame Gaston purrs with a rating of 61, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 305, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, Stringalong for South, and 5 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [305 Votes, Hall of Fame]
